    "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25",
    "summary": "Source text for 1 Chronicles 25 in Douay-Rheims Bible (Challoner)."
  },
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.1",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 1,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:1",
      "text": "Moreover David and the chief officers of the army separated for the ministry the sons of Asaph, and of Heman, and of Idithun: to prophesy with harps, and with psalteries, and with cymbals according to their number serving in their appointed office.",
      "paragraphStart": true
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.2",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 2,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:2",
      "text": "Of the sons of Asaph: Zacchur, and Joseph, and Nathania, and Asarela, sons of Asaph: under the hand of Asaph prophesying near the king.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.3",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 3,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:3",
      "text": "And of Idithun: the sons of Idithun, Godolias, Sori, Jeseias, and Hasabias, and Mathathias, under the hand of their father Idithun, who prophesied with a harp to give thanks and to praise the Lord.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.4",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 4,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:4",
      "text": "Of Heman also: the sons of Heman, Bocciau, Mathaniau, Oziel, Subuel, and Jerimoth, Hananias, Hanani, Eliatha, Geddelthi, and Romemthiezer, and Jesbacassa, Mellothi, Othir, Mahazioth:",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.5",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 5,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:5",
      "text": "All these were the sons of Heman the seer of the king in the words of God, to lift up the horn: and God gave to Heman fourteen sons and three daughters.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.6",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 6,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:6",
      "text": "All these under their father's hand were distributed to sing in the temple of the Lord, with cymbals, and psalteries and harps, for the service of the house of the Lord near the king: to wit, Asaph, and Idithun, and Heman.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.7",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 7,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:7",
      "text": "And the number of them with their brethren, that taught the song of the Lord, all the teachers, were two hundred and eighty-eight.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.8",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 8,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:8",
      "text": "And they cast lots by their courses, the elder equally with the younger, the learned and the unlearned together.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.9",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 9,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:9",
      "text": "And the first lot came forth to Joseph, who was of Asaph. The second to Godolias, to him and his sons, and his brethren twelve.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.10",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 10,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:10",
      "text": "The third to Zachur, to his sons and his brethren twelve.",
      "paragraphStart": false
    },
    {
      "id": "dra:first-chronicles.25.11",
      "translationId": "dra",
      "bookSlug": "first-chronicles",
      "chapterNumber": 25,
      "verseNumber": 11,
      "referenceLabel": "1 Chronicles 25:11",
      "text": "The fourth to Isari, to his sons and his brethren twelve.",
